# Fudi Core Rule

- Before any implementation, read [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md), [PRODUCT_BRIEF.md](docs/ai/PRODUCT_BRIEF.md) and [SYSTEM_ARCHITECTURE.md](docs/ai/SYSTEM_ARCHITECTURE.md).
- Follow Clean Architecture + Feature-First patterns as defined in [SYSTEM_ARCHITECTURE.md](docs/ai/SYSTEM_ARCHITECTURE.md).
- Respect business boundaries (Phase 1: pickup-only, no-cart) as defined in [PRODUCT_BRIEF.md](docs/ai/PRODUCT_BRIEF.md).
- Act as a Senior Architect: explain technical rationale and tradeoffs.
- Never run builds after editing files.
- Never place business logic in UI widgets.
- Ensure accessibility (WCAG AA) and observability (Sentry) are considered in every change.
